premise_source_doc_sentence: On October 7 , NWSL announced the voting results of NWSL Best XI and NWSL Second XI ; while Press and Gilliland were named to Best XI ; 5 Red Stars , Naeher , Julie Johnston , Short , Colaprico and Vanessa DiBernardo were named to NWSL Second XI .
In 2016 season , the Red Stars honored the retirements of several long time members ; Michelle Lomnicki , Julianne Sitch , Jackie Santacaterina , and Lori Chalupny .
Chicago Red Stars loaned the largest number of players to W-League , 4 more than any other NWSL club .
After the season , National team coach Jill Ellis called up 5 Red Stars , Christen Press , Alyssa Naeher , Arin Gilliland , Casey Short and Danielle Colaprico to national team training camp .
The 2015 Chicago Red Stars season is the seventh season of the soccer club and its third season in National Women 's Soccer League .
